---

<section class="company" id="company">
  <div class="wrap company__inner">
    <div class="company__lead" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">The company</span>
      <h2>A small fleet that delivers like a big one.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="company__body" data-reveal>
      <p class="company__big">
        Lelit Logistics LLC is an independent
        <span class="grad">Amazon Delivery Service Partner</span>,
        operating out of Station DOB7 in Glastonbury, Connecticut. We own the
        routes, the vans, and the standard our customers see at the door.
      </p>
      <p>
        Founded in 2026 and built by operators who came up through the cab,
        dispatch, and fleet management, we know what a good day on the road
        actually takes. We invest in training, route planning, and the
        technology that keeps every driver safe and every delivery accounted for.
      </p>
      <a href="#operation" class="company__link">See how we operate <span class="arrow">↗</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .company { padding-block: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 7rem); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); background: var(--bg-2); }
  .company__inner {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 0.85fr 1.15fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem); align-items: start;
  }
  .company__lead h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.4rem); margin-top: 1.2rem; }
  .company__big {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 1.1rem + 0.8vw, 1.75rem);
    line-height: 1.35; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; color: var(--fg);
  }
  .company__body p { color: var(--fg-soft); }
  .company__link {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5em; margin-top: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 600; color: var(--blue-soft);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--blue); padding-bottom: 3px;
    transition: gap 0.3s var(--ease);
  }
  .company__link .arrow { transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease); }
  .company__link:hover .arrow { transform: translate(3px,-3px); }

  @media (max-width: 820px) { .company__inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
